      "author": "Manisha (Manisha Kumari)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hi Monday Team,</p>\n<p>Need help regarding custom recipe automation.</p>\n<p>I just want to create a simple custom recipe of populating columns of any board.<br />\nFor example → show all columns of a board when we select a specific board.</p>\n<p>I have created a custom recipe to achieve this but it does not displaying columns of a selected board.<br />\nI am attaching screenshots as well so that anyone can understand what i am trying to achieve.<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/a/af620d6e48b81a8be7fd67dcb1e1d759f29281b9.png\" title=\"recipe board list\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/a/af620d6e48b81a8be7fd67dcb1e1d759f29281b9_2_690x377.png\" alt=\"recipe board list\" width=\"690\" height=\"377\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">recipe board list</span><span class=\"informations\">1266×693 32.3 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/8/86d7aaf4093742690d7504ca9c87c8e9189366ee.png\" title=\"recipe dependency\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/8/86d7aaf4093742690d7504ca9c87c8e9189366ee_2_689x357.png\" alt=\"recipe dependency\" width=\"689\" height=\"357\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">recipe dependency</span><span class=\"informations\">1240×642 20.7 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/3/3e63100f75690ccf78598ad2ffaa553a3f783c6a.png\" title=\"recipe sceenshot\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/3/3e63100f75690ccf78598ad2ffaa553a3f783c6a_2_690x379.png\" alt=\"recipe sceenshot\" width=\"690\" height=\"379\" /><div class=\"met