      "author": "Manisha (Manisha Kumari)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hi <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/basdebruin\">@basdebruin</a></p>\n<p>Thanks for replying.<br />\nYes you correctly got my point.<br />\ncan you please tell me how to return that array to the recipe.</p>\n<p>I did all things . like</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>first i created a custom field (test_field)<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/f/f431ebb5b27b15ceb79480df6cd58dad27418a7b.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/f/f431ebb5b27b15ceb79480df6cd58dad27418a7b_2_690x421.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"421\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">962×587 21.1 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>and then added remote url of a webhook<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/a/abd2bb5da932e204e8b431120c581be3a8ea6ab8.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/a/abd2bb5da932e204e8b431120c581be3a8ea6ab8_2_690x394.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"394\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">919×525 16.8 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p><a href=\"https://hook.eu1.make.com/uujaz4bv6b5jm6hob4p99h45q3rt5n4w\" class=\"onebox\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">https://hook.eu1.make.com/uujaz4bv6b5jm6hob4p99h45q3rt5n4w</a><br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/9/91d6c11b70e73e23b830fa0fff0437589ae2337c.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/9/91d6c11b70e73e23b830fa0fff0437589ae2337c_2_690x374.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"374\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">758×411 47.4 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>then added board id dependency<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/1/1162a48a49caaba35b4636aa2ca55e067f7216a3.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/1/1162a48a49caaba35b4636aa2ca55e067f7216a3_2_690x340.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"340\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">952×470 14.3 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>and query that board in integromat monday graphql module whenever board is selected in automation custom recipe<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/1/1840f000bc6d1139b9b31185bd3b0645cf3327ba.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/1/1840f000bc6d1139b9b31185bd3b0645cf3327ba_2_690x480.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"480\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">904×629 64.1 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>now the last part where i am stuck how to send columns after querying columns back to recipe to show under recipe dropdown( i mean * return that array to the the recipe)<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/1/16b92737b583afeb862accaaa97f54cc8cab7b95.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/1/16b92737b583afeb862accaaa97f54cc8cab7b95_2_684x500.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"684\" height=\"500\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">889×649 67 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>i want to show columns of selected board<br />\nin this recipe (screenshots are below)<br />\nlike</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>this column</strong> field in recipe should show all columns of selected board<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/b/b6566e0a0633cc932702770d7dfc329663962f1a.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/b/b6566e0a0633cc932702770d7dfc329663962f1a_2_690x310.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"310\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1197×539 10.1 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/0/02fcac7ae5ecf6677b2997207b7c058c070150f8.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/0/02fcac7ae5ecf6677b2997207b7c058c070150f8_2_690x328.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"328\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1085×516 10.5 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>as you can see from screenshots its saying first you need to select board to populate columns which is fine but when i select board from list it doesn’t display columns(that is i need to fix, please help me on this)<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/d/dfab52d8efa843ca7f02f5f7ad9e8d310f863db9.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/d/dfab52d8efa843ca7f02f5f7ad9e8d310f863db9_2_690x367.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"367\" /><div class=\"