      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hi <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/basdebruin\">@basdebruin</a></p>\n<p>please have a look on these screenshots.<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/5/5c997ba9d2f4661dc26481e338ff5ea767586162.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/5/5c997ba9d2f4661dc26481e338ff5ea767586162_2_690x250.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"250\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">897×326 21.6 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>\n<ol>\n<li>In first module is the webhook which i have given in remote url field<br />\n<img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/5/5fe1cec21edda8f76a6a2741bed3fdeb9b3fc217.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"440\" height=\"106\" /><br />\nIt generates payload board data when i select board from recipe<br />\n<img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/d/dac4d256eba0f71a5bb5ab73d92673dd6c68b614.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"644\" height=\"450\" />\n</li>\n<li>In second graph ql module , i have query all columns of that selected board<br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/b/b6020e8bc49e1be0b499209877f0f7c9db3ebc4a.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/b/b6020e8bc49e1be0b499209877f0f7c9db3ebc4a_2_690x453.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"453\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">993×652 70.8 KB</span>\n</div></a></div>\n<br />\nand it returns all columns of that board you can see in below screenshot<br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/e/eb069a2b726cdc1a6018341354ea867ab0fd07ae.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/e/eb069a2b726cdc1a6018341354ea867ab0fd07ae_2_685x500.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"685\" height=\"500\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">829×605 56.9 KB</span>\n</div></a></div>\n</li>\n<li>And in third webhook response module as you said i have added and key and value columns data<br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/9/9c5c182e27b54db9d8aff58bd708c68318b403d8.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/9/9c5c182e27b54db9d8aff58bd708c68318b403d8_2_548x500.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"548\" height=\"500\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">752×685 53.9 KB</span>\n</div></a></div>\n<br />\nand it gives 200 response their (which is fine) it displays name column<br />\n<img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/6/64e6e5de871a69ad3ac3913ece24aad829bcf729.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"555\" height=\"396\" /><br />\nbut i want to display these columns to my recipe here below screenshot<br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/d/d4a1b59267f4d73a6e12b231f18b324c4f01b875.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/d/d4a1b59267f4d73a6e12b231f18b324c4f01b875_2_690x361.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"361\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1009×528 9.24 KB</span>\n</div></a></div>\n</li>\n</ol>"
    },
