      "author": "basdebruin (Bas de Bruin)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>I’m not an Integromat expert. You need to make sure the response is formatted as [{title: “what user sees”, value: “what code receives”}]</p>\n<p>It looks you are returning an empty body, can’t you do something like this in Integromat?<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/3/31026814ceb8c3972413174523b7de2aa21a5dd8.png\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/3/31026814ceb8c3972413174523b7de2aa21a5dd8.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"441\" height=\"500\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">518×587 17.3 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>"
