      "id": 78441,
      "postNumber": 14,
      "createdAt": "2022-02-28T01:25:35.451Z",
      "author": "Manisha (Manisha Kumari)",
      "cookedHtml": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://sea1.discourse-cdn.com/monday/user_avatar/community.monday.com/basdebruin/48/688_2.png\" class=\"avatar\" /> basdebruin:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Are you sure that the endpoint to retrieve those columns is called when you click the “this column”?</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Hi <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/basdebruin\">@basdebruin</a>  Good Morning<br />\nSorry for delay, i was on weekend.<br />\nI did as you said, i added webhook response module in scenraio<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/7/74656647626760c062b654ced82ab17a40cbbe26.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/7/74656647626760c062b654ced82ab17a40cbbe26_2_690x271.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"271\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1201×473 65.5 KB</span></div></a></div><br />\nbut still when i click “this column” in recipe after selecting board first , it does not populating columns<br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/7/7f7175fd2d2525bc2fd881227bd5e1d4a681f15e.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/7/7f7175fd2d2525bc2fd881227bd5e1d4a681f15e_2_690x294.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"294\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1273×543 12.6 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>I think this is not working as you said →  \"Are you sure that the endpoint to retrieve those columns is called when you click the “this column”?</p>\n<p>what you think?</p>\n<p>I only need to add webhook url in custom test_field right?<br />\nplease see my recipe is it fine to populate columns of any board<br />\nbelow are the screenshots of my custom recipe<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/4/4510db521cf47e32ed101f62174b4a2c6817a68c.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/4/4510db521cf47e32ed101f62174b4a2c6817a68c_2_690x324.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"324\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1258×592 31.8 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/5/5c86f12bcda0fed53688ee53f1651e7c835e2f68.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/5/5c86f12bcda0fed53688ee53f1651e7c835e2f68_2_690x432.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"432\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">979×614 22.8 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/b/b34cabc5f92d0945735294c265521adbd6a3b9ee.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/b/b34cabc5f92d0945735294c265521adbd6a3b9ee_2_664x500.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"664\" height=\"500\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">751×565 19.2 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/f/ff4eecc082bcce3a68ad071b42098f33b051d964.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/f/ff4eecc082bcce3a6